            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1977,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01A5GxTN4ad75AnJuahpX2u9\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"helpMe\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Perfect! Let me help you get specific about who you're selling to and what keeps them up at night.\\\",\\n  \\\"template\\\": \\\"**1. Who are they?**\\\\n[Job title/role] at [company size/type] who [specific context about their work]\\\\n\\\\n**2. What's their main pain point?**\\\\nThey spend [time/effort] on [specific task], which [emotional impact: frustrates/exhausts/delays them]\\\\n\\\\n**3. What are they actually trying to achieve?**\\\\nThey want to [specific outcome] so they can [bigger goal/benefit]\\\\n\\\\n**4. Why doesn't this work today?**\\\\nCurrent solutions [describe the gap: too manual, too expensive, too slow, etc.]\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n\\\\n**Fill this in for your business:**\\\\nThink about the person who would pay you money. What's their job? What does a typical week look like? What frustrates them most about finding guests right now?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"**1. Who:** Podcast hosts with 10K-100K monthly listeners who run shows independently or with small teams\\\\n\\\\n**2. Pain point:** They spend 5-10 hours per week manually searching LinkedIn, Twitter, and email lists trying to find guests who fit their niche, and half the time the guest says no or doesn't show up\\\\n\\\\n**3. Goal:** They want to fill their content calendar with relevant, credible guests so they can focus on recording and growing their audience instead of being a talent scout\\\\n\\\\n**4. Why it fails now:** Guest databases are outdated, cold outreach has low response rates, and agencies are too expensive for independent creators\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2807,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":414,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
